Sentencas: A mathematical model of a tubular solid oxide fuel cell is presented.
Titulo: A MATHEMATICAL-MODEL OF A SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELL

Sentencas: The complete electrochemical and thermal factors are accounted for in a rigorous manner.
Titulo: A MATHEMATICAL-MODEL OF A SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELL

Sentencas: All required parameters are determined from independent sources; none are fit from performance data.
Titulo: A MATHEMATICAL-MODEL OF A SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELL

Sentencas: To verify the accuracy of the model predictions, comparison is made with single cell test data from Westinghouse.
Titulo: A MATHEMATICAL-MODEL OF A SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELL

Sentencas: Agreement with electrochemical and thermal results are within 5%, and for most points, much better.
Titulo: A MATHEMATICAL-MODEL OF A SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELL

Sentencas: Predictions are shown for power-voltage, irreversibilities, and temperature and current distributions under various conditions.
Titulo: A MATHEMATICAL-MODEL OF A SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELL
